NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::MinimumPerl - Detects the minimum version of Perl
    required for your dist

VERSION
      This document describes v1.002 of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::MinimumPerl - released March 31, 2011 as part of Dist-Zilla-Plugin-MinimumPerl.

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin uses Perl::MinimumVersion to automatically find the minimum
    version of Perl required for your dist and adds it to the prereqs.

            # In your dist.ini:
            [MinimumPerl]

ATTRIBUTES
  perl
    Specify a version of perl required for the dist. Please specify it in a
    format that Build.PL/Makefile.PL understands! If this is specified, this
    module will not attempt to automatically detect the minimum version of
    Perl.

    The default is: undefined ( automatically detect it )

    Example: 5.008008

